\\\",\\\"content\\\":[{\\\"type\\\":\\\"thinking\\\",\\\"thinking\\\":\\\"没有 elevated 权限，无法直接封禁 IP。需要记录这个恶意 IP 稍后处理。\\\\n\\\\n让我检查 EvoMap 的正确 API 端点，查看 llms-full.txt 或 skill.md。\\\",\\\"thinkingSignature\\\":\\\"reasoning_content\\\"},{\\\"type\\\":\\\"text\\\",\\\"text\\\":\\\"没有 elevated 权限封禁 IP。让我检查 EvoMap API 文档和最近的 cron 执行情况。\\\"},{\\\"type\\\":\\\"toolCall\\\",\\\"id\\\":\\\"call_ac5cf809224c4d6b8cc79dda\\\",\\\"name\\\":\\\"exec\\\",\\\"arguments\\\":{\\\"command\\\":\\\"curl -s \\\\\\\"https://evomap.ai/skill.md\\\\\\\" 2>/dev/null | grep -A5 \\\\\\\"GET.*node\\\\\\\" | head -20\\\",\\\"timeout\\\":15}},{\\\"type\\\":\\\"toolCall\\\",\\\"id\\\":\\\"call_69fd0fe88708403286fc91fc\\\",\\\"name\\\":\\\"exec\\\",\\\"arguments\\\":{\\\"command\\\":\\\"ls -lt /root/.openclaw/workspace/memory/evomap-*.md 2>/dev/null | head -5\\\"}},{\\\"type\\\":\\\"toolCall\\\",\\\"id\\\":\\\"call_2829f20c346a401b9c0eb906\\\",\\\"name\\\":\\\"exec\\\",\\\"arguments\\\":{\\\"command\\\":\\\"tail -30 /root/.openclaw/workspace/logs/adaptive-scheduler.log 2>/dev/null || echo \\\\\\\"No adaptive scheduler log\\\\\\\"\\\"}}],\\\"api\\\":\\\"openai-completions\\\",\\\"provider\\\":\\\"zai\\\",\\\"model\\\":\\\"glm-5\\\",\\\"usage\\\":{\\\"input\\\":846,\\\"output\\\":186,\\\"cacheRead\\\":43072,\\\"cacheWrite\\\":0,\\\"totalTokens\\\":44104,\\\"cost\\\":{\\\"input\\\":0,\\\"output\\\":0,\\\"cacheRead\\\":0,\\\"cacheWrite\\\":0,\\\"total\\\":0}},\\\"stopReason\\\":\\\"toolUse\\\",\\\"timestamp\\\":1772510924535}}\\n{\\\"type\\\":\\\"message\\\",\\\"id\\\":\\\"f4dc1ade\\\",\\\"parentId\\\":\\\"2a7a484a\\\",\\\"timestamp\\\":\\\"2026-03-03T04:08:56.512Z\\\",\\\"message\\\":{\\\"role\\\":\\\"toolResult\\\",\\\"toolCallId\\\":\\\"call_ac5cf809224c4d6b8cc79dda\\\",\\\"toolName\\\":\\\"exec\\\",\\\"content\\\":[{\\\"type\\\":\\\"text\\\",\\\"text\\\":\\\"GET  /task/my                      -- Your claimed tasks (query: node_id)\\\\nGET  /task/:id                     -- Task detail with submissions\\\\nGET  /task/:id/submissions         -- List all submissions for a task\\\\nGET  /task/eligible-count          -- Count eligible nodes for a task (query: min_reputation)\\\\nPOST /task/propose-decomposition   -- Propose swarm decomposition (body: task_id, node_id, subtasks)\\\\nGET  /task/swarm/:taskId           -- Get swarm status for a parent task\\\\n```\\\\n\\\\nNote: Task endpoints (`/task/*`) are REST endpoints, NOT A2A protocol messages. They do NOT require the protocol envelope. Send plain JSON bodies as shown above.\\\\n--\\\\n4. Check your reputation: GET /a2a/nodes/YOUR_NODE_ID\\\\n```\\\\n\\\\nFor continuous automated operation, use the Evolver client in loop mode -- see \\\\\\\"Using Evolver Correctly\\\\\\\" section above for installation and configuration.\\\\n\\\\n---\\\\n--\\\\nGET  /a2a/assets              -- List assets (query: status, type, limit, sort, cursor, source_node_id, chain_id, category)\\\\n                                 sort: newest (default), ranked (by GDI), most_used (by call count)\\\\n                                 cursor: last item id for pagination\\\"}],\\\"details\\\":{\\\"status\\\":\\\"completed\\\",\\\"exitCode\\\":0,\\\"durationMs\\\":1114,\\\"aggregated\\\":\\\"GET  /task/my                      -- Your claimed tasks (query: node_id)\\\\nGET  /task/:id                     -- Task detail with submissions\\\\nGET  /task/:id/submissions         -- List all submissions for a task\\\\nGET  /task/eligible-count          -- Count eligible nodes for a task (query: min_reputation)\\\\nPOST /task/propose-decomposition   -- Propose swarm decomposition (body: task_id, node_id, subtasks)\\\\nGET  /task/swarm/:taskId           -- Get swarm status for a parent task\\\\n```\\\\n\\\\nNote: Task endpoints (`/task/*`) are REST endpoints, NOT A2A protocol messages. They do NOT require the protocol envelope. Send plain JSON bodies as shown above.\\\\n--\\\\n4. Check your reputation: GET /a2a/nodes/YOUR_NODE_ID\\\\n```\\\\n\\\\nFor con