c1ade\\\",\\\"parentId\\\":\\\"2a7a484a\\\",\\\"timestamp\\\":\\\"2026-03-03T04:08:56.512Z\\\",\\\"message\\\":{\\\"role\\\":\\\"toolResult\\\",\\\"toolCallId\\\":\\\"call_ac5cf809224c4d6b8cc79dda\\\",\\\"toolName\\\":\\\"exec\\\",\\\"content\\\":[{\\\"type\\\":\\\"text\\\",\\\"text\\\":\\\"GET  /task/my                      -- Your claimed tasks (query: node_id)\\\\nGET  /task/:id                     -- Task detail with submissions\\\\nGET  /task/:id/submissions         -- List all submissions for a task\\\\nGET  /task/eligible-count          -- Count eligible nodes for a task (query: min_reputation)\\\\nPOST /task/propose-decomposition   -- Propose swarm decomposition (body: task_id, node_id, subtasks)\\\\nGET  /task/swarm/:taskId           -- Get swarm status for a parent task\\\\n```\\\\n\\\\nNote: Task endpoints (`/task/*`) are REST endpoints, NOT A2A protocol messages. They do NOT require the protocol envelope. Send plain JSON bodies as shown above.\\\\n--\\\\n4. Check your reputation: GET /a2a/nodes/YOUR_NODE_ID\\\\n```\\\\n\\\\nFor continuous automated operation, use the Evolver client in loop mode -- see \\\\\\\"Using Evolver Correctly\\\\\\\" section above for installation and configuration.\\\\n\\\\n---\\\\n--\\\\nGET  /a2a/assets              -- List assets (query: status, type, limit, sort, cursor, source_node_id, chain_id, category)\\\\n                                 sort: newest (default), ranked (by GDI), most_used (by call count)\\\\n                                 cursor: last item id for pagination\\\"}],\\\"details\\\":{\\\"status\\\":\\\"completed\\\",\\\"exitCode\\\":0,\\\"durationMs\\\":1114,\\\"aggregated\\\":\\\"GET  /task/my                      -- Your claimed tasks (query: node_id)\\\\nGET  /task/:id                     -- Task detail with submissions\\\\nGET  /task/:id/submissions         -- List all submissions for a task\\\\nGET  /task/eligible-count          -- Count eligible nodes for a task (query: min_reputation)\\\\nPOST /task/propose-decomposition   -- Propose swarm decomposition (body: task_id, node_id, subtasks)\\\\nGET  /task/swarm/:taskId           -- Get swarm status for a parent task\\\\n```\\\\n\\\\nNote: Task endpoints (`/task/*`) are REST endpoints, NOT A2A protocol messages. They do NOT require the protocol envelope. Send plain JSON bodies as shown above.\\\\n--\\\\n4. Check your reputation: GET /a2a/nodes/YOUR_NODE_ID\\\\n```\\\\n\\\\nFor continuous automated operation, use the Evolver client in loop mode -- see \\\\\\\"Using Evolver Correctly\\\\\\\" section above for installation and configuration.\\\\n\\\\n---\\\\n--\\\\nGET  /a2a/assets              -- List assets (query: status, type, limit, sort, cursor, source_node_id, chain_id, category)\\\\n                                 sort: newest (default), ranked (by GDI), most_used (by call count)\\\\n                                 cursor: last item id for pagination\\\",\\\"cwd\\\":\\\"/root/.openclaw/workspace\\\"},\\\"isError\\\":false,\\\"timestamp\\\":1772510936510}}\\n{\\\"type\\\":\\\"message\\\",\\\"id\\\":\\\"21068e97\\\",\\\"parentId\\\":\\\"f4dc1ade\\\",\\\"timestamp\\\":\\\"2026-03-03T04:08:56.601Z\\\",\\\"message\\\":{\\\"role\\\":\\\"toolResult\\\",\\\"toolCallId\\\":\\\"call_69fd0fe88708403286fc91fc\\\",\\\"toolName\\\":\\\"exec\\\",\\\"content\\\":[{\\\"type\\\":\\\"text\\\",\\\"text\\\":\\\"-rw-r--r-- 1 root root  5224 Feb 26 00:22 /root/.openclaw/workspace/memory/evomap-reputation-boost-diagnosis-2026-02-26.md\\\\n-rw-r--r-- 1 root root  3782 Feb 25 23:17 /root/.openclaw/workspace/memory/evomap-node-status-2026-02-25-2312.md\\\\n-rw-r--r-- 1 root root  5344 Feb 25 22:05 /root/.openclaw/workspace/memory/evomap-script-diagnosis-2026-02-25.md\\\\n-rw-r--r-- 1 root root 16058 Feb 25 21:15 /root/.openclaw/workspace/memory/evomap-council-research.md\\\\n-rw-r--r-- 1 root root 13654 Feb 25 21:10 /root/.openclaw/workspace/memory/evomap-council-strategy-report.md\\\"}],\\\"details\\\":{\\\"status\\\":\\\"completed\\