{"type":"compaction","id":"fc6e5b5c","parentId":"d811bccb","timestamp":"2026-03-03T12:04:27.873Z","summary":"## Goal\n- Execute deep log analysis cron task (evolver-log-analysis) to proactively discover system issues\n- Analyze session logs from `/root/.openclaw/agents/main/sessions/*.jsonl` for the past 6 hours\n- Generate detailed analysis reports with severity-ranked issues (P0/P1/P2/P3)\n- Update evolution-history and pattern-registry.md with findings\n\n## Constraints & Preferences\n- Must analyze full 6 hours, not just recent 30 minutes\n- Focus on: errors, warnings, timeouts, API failures, resource anomalies\n- Must generate report files, not just summarize in chat\n- Must update pattern-registry.md if new patterns discovered\n- Don't just say \"system stable\" - actively dig for potential issues\n\n## Progress\n### Done\n- [x] Round 266 (12:00): Discovered PAT-059 - API 401 authentication failure (613 errors), all 8 cron tasks failing\n- [x] Round 267 (16:00): Confirmed API 401 issue resolved, system recovered to 7.5/10 health score\n- [x] Created `/root/.openclaw/workspace/memory/log-analysis-2026-03-03-1200.md`\n- [x] Created `/root/.openclaw/workspace/memory/log-analysis-2026-03-03-1600.md`\n- [x] Created `/root/.openclaw/workspace/evolver_history/projects/openclaw/rounds/round-266-20260303-1200/report.md`\n- [x] Created `/root/.openclaw/workspace/evolver_history/projects/openclaw/rounds/round-267-20260303-1600/report.md`\n- [x] Updated `/root/.openclaw/workspace/evolver/pattern-registry.md` with PAT-059 (now marked recovered)\n- [x] Updated `/root/.openclaw/workspace/memory/2026-03-03.md`\n\n### In Progress\n- [ ] Block malicious IP `45.156.87.205` (requires elevated permissions)\n- [ ] Update EvoMap scripts to use correct API endpoints\n\n### Blocked\n- Cannot block malicious IP due to missing elevated permissions in heartbeat context\n\n## Key Decisions\n- **PAT-059 Status Update**: Changed from 🔴 Emergency to 🟢 Recovered after confirming 0 new 401 errors in 12:00-16:00 timeframe\n- **Health Score**: Restored from 1.0 (critical) to 7.5 (good) after API recovery\n\n## Next Steps\n1. Block malicious IP: `sudo iptables -I INPUT -s 45.156.87.205 -j DROP`\n2. Update EvoMap scripts to use `/a2a/nodes/{node_id}` instead of deprecated `/api/nodes/{node_id}`\n3. Continue monitoring for API 401 errors in next analysis round (20:00)\n\n## Critical Context\n- **API 401 Recovery Timeline**: ~65 errors (00:00-08:00) → ~2 errors (08:00-12:00) → 0 errors (12:00-16:00)\n- **Malicious IP**: `45.156.87.205` scanning `.env` files (all returned 404, no data leaked)\n- **Deprecated EvoMap Endpoints**: `/api/nodes/{node_id}`, `/api/leaderboard`\n- **Correct EvoMap Endpoints**: `GET /a2a/nodes/{node_id}`, `GET /api/health`\n- **Current System State**: Memory 52%, Disk 72%, CPU 0.13, Uptime ~6 days\n- **Pattern Registry Path**: `/root/.openclaw/workspace/evolver/pattern-registry.md`\n- **Log Analysis Report Path Pattern**: `/root/.openclaw/workspace/memory/log-analysis-YYYY-MM-DD-HHMM.md`\n\n---\n\n**Turn Context (split turn):**\n\n## Goal\n- Execute deep log analysis task for OpenClaw agent system\n- Analyze session logs from the last 6 hours (14:00-20:00 on March 3rd, 2026)\n- Identify error patterns, performance issues, API failures (401/403/429/500), configuration problems, and workflow issues\n- Generate report file at `/root/.openclaw/workspace/memory/log-analysis-2026-03-03-2000.md`\n- Update evolution history at `/root/.openclaw/workspace/evolver_history/projects/openclaw/rounds/`\n- Update pattern-registry.md if new patterns are discovered\n\n## Constraints & Preferences\n- Must analyze the full 6-hour window, not just recent 30 minutes\n- Must not provide a \"lightweight check\" - need deep investigation\n- Must proactively discover potential issues even if no obvious errors\n- Report format required: statistics, problems (sorted by P0/P1/P2/P3 severity), details, improvement suggestions\n- Current time: Tuesday, March 3rd, 2026 — 8:00 PM (Asia/Shanghai)\n\n## Progress\n### Done\n- [x] Found 12 log files modified in last 6 hours\n- [x] Checked system resources: Memory 56% (2055 MB), Disk 72%, CPU 0.00, Uptime 6 days 3 hours\n- [x] Identified 21 errors in session d4382a89-e67b-4339-ba63-db63f4f2cb28.jsonl\n- [x] Found stopReason distribution: 2 \"error\", 2 \"stop\", 25 \"toolUse\"\n- [x] Discovered 401 error count reduced from 613 (at 12:00) to just 2 in recent session\n\n### In Progress\n- [ ] Deep error pattern analysis across all 12 session files\n- [ ] Checking for 401/403/429/500 errors in 14:00-20:00 timeframe\n- [ ] Generating comprehensive log analysis report\n- [ ] Updating evolution history and pattern registry\n\n### Blocked\n- None currently\n\n## Key Decisions\n- **Previous P0 Issue (PAT-059)**: API 401 authentication failures that caused 613 errors and blocked all cron tasks - appears to be recovering (only 2 errors in recent session)\n- **Session focus**: d4382a89 session has the most activity with 25 toolUse stops and 21 errors to investigate\n\n## Next Steps\n1. Complete error pattern analysis for all 12 log files in the 14:00-20:00 timeframe\n2. Check for any 401/403/429/500/timeout errors specifically in the recent time window\n3. Analyze stopReason patterns across all sessions\n4. Generate comprehensive report at `/root/.openclaw/workspace/memory/log-analysis-2026-03-03-2000.md`\n5. Update evolution history directory\n6. Update pattern-registry.md if new patterns discovered\n\n## Critical Context\n- **Log file path**: `/root/.openclaw/agents/main/sessions/*.jsonl`\n- **12 log files found**: d4382a89 (most recent, 20:00), 6c883048, 6bd27fa9, and 9 others from 16:11-20:00\n- **Previous report**: `/root/.openclaw/workspace/memory/log-analysis-2026-03-03-1200.md` documented 613 401 errors\n- **Current grep command result**: `grep -c \"stopReason.*stop\"` returned 23 successful stops\n- **Error types to watch**: 401 (authentication), 403 (forbidden), 429 (rate limit), 500 (